		"description": "The **Product Rating & Review Service** provides APIs that allow users to submit, view, update, and delete product reviews and ratings. This service is essential for enabling user-generated feedback in e-commerce platforms or any application where customer input is valuable.\n\n---\n\n### Key Features\n\n- ‚≠ê **Submit Ratings & Reviews**\n    \n    Users can post a rating (1‚Äì5 stars) and a written review for any product.\n    \n- üìÑ **View Reviews**\n    \n    Retrieve all reviews for a specific product or a single review by ID.\n    \n- ‚úèÔ∏è **Edit Reviews**\n    \n    Users can update their own reviews if necessary.\n    \n- ‚ùå **Delete Reviews**\n    \n    Support for removing reviews when needed (e.g., spam or user request).",
